hdot&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Ffeatures.slashdot.org%2Farticle.pl%3Fsid%3D05%2F04%2F18%2F164213%26tid%3D95%26tid%3D149%26tid%3D9&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/ja.wikipedia.org:%E3%83%A9%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%83%BB%E3%82%B5%E3%83%B3%E3%82%AC%E3%83%BC"><span style="display: none;"> </span></span>—Larry Sanger.<br/> •
